OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773034803
OL,3,CWomen 'dehumanised and diminished' by
OL,4,Cinadequate care after miscarriage `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FWomen who suffer miscarriages are
OL,8,Fbeing put at risk of further harm and
OL,9,Fdistress by a lack of adequate follow-
OL,10,Fup care, according to a report.
OL,12,FOne patient described her experience
OL,13,Fas "dehumanising", with others warning
OL,14,Fwomen are being dismissed and
OL,15,Ftraumatised.
OL,26,@uD@DOUuD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773034803
OL,3,CWomen 'dehumanised and diminished' by
OL,4,Cinadequate care after miscarriage `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FIt comes as research by the
OL,8,FMiscarriage Association found almost
OL,9,Ftwo-thirds of women felt follow-up
OL,10,Fcare was not adequate, while more than
OL,11,Ffour in 10 who wanted treatment for
OL,12,Fmental health issues after losing
OL,13,Ftheir baby did not receive it.
OL,15,FThe new report, which has been backed
OL,16,Fby MPs and TV and radio presenter
OL,17,FMyleene Klass, is calling for urgent
OL,18,Faction to ensure follow-up care
OL,19,Ffollowing a miscarriage is routine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773034803
OL,3,CWomen 'dehumanised and diminished' by
OL,4,Cinadequate care after miscarriage `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThe research included more than 1,000
OL,8,Fpeople in the UK impacted by
OL,9,Fmiscarriage before the 24th week of
OL,10,Fpregnancy.
OL,12,FWhile more than half described their
OL,13,Fcare as good or excellent, more than a
OL,14,Fquarter said it was poor or very poor.
OL,16,FSome 65% said they did not have
OL,17,Fadequate follow-up care, while 42%
OL,18,Fsaid they did not receive treatment
OL,19,Ffor mental health symptoms following
OL,20,Ftheir miscarriage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773034803
OL,3,CWomen 'dehumanised and diminished' by
OL,4,Cinadequate care after miscarriage `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FMany women felt they were sent home
OL,8,Fwith little or no guidance, or with
OL,9,Fconflicting advice, according to the
OL,10,FMiscarriage Association.
OL,12,FSome reported insensitive wording from
OL,13,Fhealthcare professionals, with one
OL,14,Fwoman claiming she was told her baby
OL,15,F"had been put in the incinerator with
OL,16,Fthe rest of the medical waste" whilst
OL,17,Frecovering from a ruptured ectopic
OL,18,Fpregnancy.
OL,26,@wD@AOUxD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773034803
OL,3,CWomen 'dehumanised and diminished' by
OL,4,Cinadequate care after miscarriage `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThe report also found access to
OL,8,Fservices such as early pregnancy units
OL,9,Fand scans was inconsistent.
OL,11,FIt added that a "recurring theme was a
OL,12,Flack of dignity", with some women left
OL,13,Fwithout access to basic care, such as
OL,14,Fsanitary pads.
OL,16,FVicki Robinson, chief executive of the
OL,17,FMiscarriage Association, said: "Too
OL,18,Fmany women and their partners are
OL,19,Fbeing failed by a system that is
OL,20,Finconsistent, unequal and too often
OL,21,Fdictated by chance or circumstance.
OL,26,@sD@QOUtD@PO]yD@`OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773034803
OL,3,CWomen 'dehumanised and diminished' by
OL,4,Cinadequate care after miscarriage `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"People told us they felt unheard and
OL,8,Fdiminished, caught between gaps in
OL,9,Fhealthcare, uncertainty at work, and a
OL,10,Fwider silence that leaves miscarriage
OL,11,Fpoorly understood and acknowledged.
OL,13,F"This is not about blaming
OL,14,Findividuals. Many examples of
OL,15,Fcompassionate care exist, and we are
OL,16,Fworking to build on these through our
OL,17,Ffree specialist training for
OL,18,Fhealthcare professionals.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773034803
OL,3,CWomen 'dehumanised and diminished' by
OL,4,Cinadequate care after miscarriage `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"But when support depends on where you
OL,8,Fare, who you speak to, or how well
OL,9,Fsystems join up, too many people are
OL,10,Fleft facing additional physical harm
OL,11,Fand lasting psychological distress at
OL,12,Fan already vulnerable time."
OL,14,FLabour MP Sarah Owen, chairwoman of
OL,15,Fthe Women and Equalities Committee and
OL,16,FMiscarriage Association ambassador,
OL,17,Fadded: "Losing a pregnancy at any
OL,18,Fstage makes a woman physically and
OL,19,Fmentally vulnerable.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@\O]yD@HOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773034803
OL,3,CWomen 'dehumanised and diminished' by
OL,4,Cinadequate care after miscarriage `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"It's shocking to hear their stories
OL,8,Fof being treated with such
OL,9,Finsensitivity by trained healthcare
OL,10,Fproviders, adding harm to what is
OL,11,Falready such a traumatic experience.
OL,13,F"While we welcome the excellent care
OL,14,Fsome trusts have provided, the report
OL,15,Fshows that far too many women have
OL,16,Fgone neglected, mistreated, or even
OL,17,Fleft with permanent health problems.
OL,18,FBereaved parents must have equal
OL,19,Faccess to the best possible care
OL,20,Fregardless of where they live."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU|D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773034803
OL,3,CWomen 'dehumanised and diminished' by
OL,4,Cinadequate care after miscarriage `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThe research also included experiences
OL,8,Fof miscarriage and the workplace.
OL,10,FPeople told the Miscarriage
OL,11,FAssociation that "awareness and formal
OL,12,Fpolicies around baby loss remain
OL,13,Flimited, and employees' rights around
OL,14,Fpregnancy are poorly understood".
OL,16,FThey said "fear of stigma or career
OL,17,Fimpact" is also preventing people from
OL,18,Fopenly discussing the issue.
OL,26,@sD@ROUvD@`O]xD@KOUyD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773034803
OL,3,CWomen 'dehumanised and diminished' by
OL,4,Cinadequate care after miscarriage `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FKlass, who is a champion of the
OL,8,FMiscarriage Association and received
OL,9,Fan MBE for her campaigning on
OL,10,Fmiscarriage, said: "Pregnancy loss is
OL,11,Fnot a niche issue, it affects
OL,12,Fthousands each year.
OL,14,F"Yet many still struggle to access the
OL,15,Fcare and understanding they deserve.
OL,26,@rD@TOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773034803
OL,3,CWomen 'dehumanised and diminished' by
OL,4,Cinadequate care after miscarriage `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"This research by the Miscarriage
OL,8,FAssociation is an important step in
OL,9,Fholding the system to account and
OL,10,Fpushing for meaningful change. We must
OL,11,Flisten to those with lived experience
OL,12,Fand make miscarriage care a priority."
OL,14,FThe report has made a number of
OL,15,Frecommendations, including ensuring
OL,16,Fthat follow-up care becomes routine
OL,17,Ffor every miscarriage, with opening
OL,18,Fhours at early pregnancy units
OL,19,Fextended to provide more access to
OL,20,Ftimely care.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773034803
OL,3,CWomen 'dehumanised and diminished' by
OL,4,Cinadequate care after miscarriage `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FIt also calls for more bereavement
OL,8,Fsupport and urges workplaces to
OL,9,Fimplement the right to bereavement
OL,10,Fleave.
OL,12,FMs Robinson added: "Change must be
OL,13,Fsystemic. Clear, consistent aftercare
OL,14,Ffollowing pregnancy loss should be
OL,15,Favailable to all.
OL,17,F"Until pregnancy loss is properly
OL,18,Facknowledged, too many people will
OL,19,Fcontinue to face miscarriage without
OL,20,Fthe care, support and recognition they
OL,21,Fneed and deserve."
OL,26,@tD@TOUyD@AOU}D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773034803
OL,3,CWomen 'dehumanised and diminished' by
OL,4,Cinadequate care after miscarriage `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,8,Fspokesperson described losing a baby
OL,9,Fas "heartbreaking" and said the
OL,10,Freport's findings were "unacceptable".
OL,12,FThe spokesperson said: "We are working
OL,13,Fto improve miscarriage care to ensure
OL,14,Fwomen get the support they need, and
OL,15,Fwe have already extended the reach of
OL,16,Fbaby loss certificates to provide the
OL,17,Frecognition that can mean so much to
OL,18,Faffected families.
OL,26,@qD@DOUqD@RO]rD@XOUrD@eO]tD@XOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
